r-pok-unrest/articleshow/131724370.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/watch-thousands-of-british-kashmiris-protest-outside-uk-parliament-over-pok-unrest/articleshow/131724370.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-14T21:38:23+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131724431,imgsize-1837105.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Indian-origin men treating murder weapon ‘like a trophy’ after killing elderly Canadian couple]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131723637.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/court-releases-video-of-indian-origin-men-who-brutally-killed-elderly-canadian-couple-showed-murder-weapon-like-a-trophy/articleshow/131723637.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/court-releases-video-of-indian-origin-men-who-brutally-killed-elderly-canadian-couple-showed-murder-weapon-like-a-trophy/articleshow/131723637.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-14T20:38:01+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131723726,imgsize-137088.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Six killed after two helicopters collide mid-air in Rio de Janeiro; video]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131723137.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Tragedy struck western Rio de Janeiro as two helicopters collided mid-air, claiming at least six lives. The devastating crash ignited a massive fire at an electric car dealership, engulfing numerous vehicles. Firefighters battled the blaze, which sp